description: The people of Kansas City have spoken, and they’re saying that Vee’s BBQ & Casual Catering is where you’ll find some of the best BBQ you may ever taste. It’s actually no surprise when you see how much care and quality the Vee’s team puts into their meaty cuisine. They’re serving up a succulent selection of BBQ ribs, beef brisket, wings, smoked turkey, smoked sausage, chicken, pulled pork, and rib-tips. This deliciousness is perfect for every kind of party, so if you’re looking for some great homestyle cooking for your next event, you just need to have Vee’s come cater!
name: Vee's BBQ & Casual Catering
